Interface AuthenticationMechanismResultPauseTask

All Superinterfaces:

public interface AuthenticationMechanismResultPauseTask extends AuthenticationMechanismResultTask
This interface represents a pause task. Pause task is contained in authentication pause result returned by authentication mechanism.
